{"tid":1364740,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「元朗地理」水邊村同水邊村遊樂場係兩個地方黎架！","createTime":"2019-07-25T12:19:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T17:42:20.000Z","uid":4186,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7b0573ea7f56340cf2b76968facf22256c299748","tid":1364740,"uid":4186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:19:18.000Z","msg":"身為元朗足球撚，聽講水邊個場舖左人造草地，見到咁多位兄弟想入黎試下個草地，就一定唔可以去錯場阿！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/soyzOAd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsoyzOAd.png&h=c0397109&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n地圖左上角為水邊圍邨<br />\n地圖右下角為水邊圍遊樂場<br />\n<br />\n中間路程大約5分鐘，<br />\n但人多+等燈就可能要耐啲啦，<br />\n所以唔好去錯場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外，<br />\n因為今次係草地波，大家務必帶好裝備，人地一個收山腳踢埋黎就麻煩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0fc5d2dc46481edbc38ead965076b965613368c","tid":1364740,"uid":278712,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:20:32.000Z","msg":"兄弟踢波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a4aa2e0a6ec831d09a66d5e7f095ebf236c3e2f","tid":1364740,"uid":4186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:20:34.000Z","msg":"去錯場就要行返過黎，好撚煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e981652cabe5a36fe29aa52753554cfc2c4aa77","tid":1364740,"uid":38833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:22:17.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n其實好多人平時黎元朗買餸嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1364551/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1364551/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"244ea2aad8d62806f9fc4113556a142cd2ac5a28","tid":1364740,"uid":42629,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:22:33.000Z","msg":"你自己2個地方名啲字都打錯哂<br />\n睇黎得你搞錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a00e8fc27ca8154daef036390ba1c8936f225d29","tid":1364740,"uid":4186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:23:50.000Z","msg":"另外交通方面，<br />\n巴士可以元朗公園站/元朗廣場（食左野先）落，<br />\n西鐵既話就兩個搭法：<br />\n1. 元朗站落，落去搭任何一架輕鐵同元朗廣場站/水邊圍站（水邊圍站落既野就要上天橋過返黎，唔係既話可以跨欄直接過黎）<br />\n2. 朗屏站落行過黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"072f32c81c30e8bad3b94d063b6abcabe8df4293","tid":1364740,"uid":4186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"244ea2aad8d62806f9fc4113556a142cd2ac5a28","tid":1364740,"uid":42629,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:22:33.000Z","msg":"你自己2個地方名啲字都打錯哂<br />\n睇黎得你搞錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:24:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />柒左sorry"},{"pid":"3cce318685d9530b1afb06c004601eeb47a87d4b","tid":1364740,"uid":13492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:24:33.000Z","msg":"踢草地波？我有無聽錯<br />\nbtw fyr對面係元朗警署<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2c7a09d3e6d60503c94bd818cc5d3ccfdfcd064","tid":1364740,"uid":4186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3cce318685d9530b1afb06c004601eeb47a87d4b","tid":1364740,"uid":13492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:24:33.000Z","msg":"踢草地波？我有無聽錯<br />\nbtw fyr對面係元朗警署<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:25:38.000Z","msg":"星期六舖完啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b037bb14fdcbc0ddd92fefb5f7c128c583350e2d","tid":1364740,"uid":13492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e2c7a09d3e6d60503c94bd818cc5d3ccfdfcd064","tid":1364740,"uid":4186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3cce318685d9530b1afb06c004601